# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation VAR++ LAUNCHER OBFUSCATION - Security
# Author: Timur Zinniatullin, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-13
# Level: high
# Description: Detects Obfuscated Powershell via VAR++ LAUNCHER
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/win_security_invoke_obfuscation_via_var_services_security.yml

EventID=4697 ServiceFileName IN ("*{0}*", "*{1}*", "*{2}*", "*{3}*", "*{4}*", "*{5}*") ServiceFileName="*&&set*" ServiceFileName="*cmd*" ServiceFileName="*/c*" ServiceFileName="*-f*"